      solution        : "If you have deployed IS-IS in your network and have enabled loose authentication checking, re-enable it by issuing the following command from the [edit protocols isis] hierarchy:
    [edit protocols isis]
    user@host#delete loose-authentication-check

    Default Value:
    No IS-IS routing is configured by default."
