For most platforms SSH-ECDSA, SSH-ED25519, SSH-DSS (1024 bit DSA keys) and SSH-RSA are permitted by default.
SSH-DSS is not supported on JUNOS in FIPS Mode, so cannot be enabled in FIPS mode."
